<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`If we served `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`index.html`}</MDXTag>{` and `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`bundle.js`}</MDXTag>{` from a Content Server, we can make that server work with no auth req'd.`}</MDXTag>
